ActControlled Drugs and Substances Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule I to the Controlled Drugs and Substances Act (Tramadol)
PrecisOrder Amending Schedule I to the CONTROLLED DRUGS AND SUBSTANCES ACT (TRAMADOL) in order to add tramadol, M1, M1, and the salts, isomers, and salts of isomers of tramadol M1, M5 to the list of substances.
